subject: Automobile Racing
Engines
organizations: National Assn of Stock Car Auto Racing
lead_paragraph: Jeff Gordon overcame an overheating engine and, with steam pouring out of his racecar, pulled away to win the Dodge Avenger 500 at Darlington Raceway.
